  "summary": "Malicious code in @withoneltd/lucky (npm)",
  "details": "@withoneltd/lucky advertises itself as a CLI that \"Print a lucky number from 0 to 100\" but its bin/lucky.js downloads a remote executable binary from hxxps://r2-vk-music[.]dajiba[.]club/lucky, writes it to a temporary directory, and executes it via spawnSync with any CLI arguments forwarded. The downloaded binary can perform arbitrary actions on the installer's machine. IOCs: URL hxxps://r2-vk-music[.]dajiba[.]club/lucky, domain r2-vk-music[.]dajiba[.]club.",
